ation above\n3. Ensure proper YAML formatting and indentation\n4. Verify all configuration sections are included\n5. Report status as DONE when complete\n\nFocus only on creating this configuration file exactly as specified."},"uuid":"e5513c68-befd-4fd9-9b41-68905c30dc60","timestamp":"2026-03-23T13:22:21.272Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"/Users/xpeng/Desktop/workSpace/XPMotors_IOS","sessionId":"b9f2b222-0dec-4a0c-91a6-0140ed9cc86f","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"vehicle/5.20.0-perf-opt","slug":"synchronous-wobbling-glacier"}
